li><a href=\"https://wicg.github.io/element-timing/\">Spec - Element Timing API</a></li>","updatedAt":"2020-06-23T00:06:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Rendering metrics</h2><h3>(Hero) Element Timing</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://speedcurve.com/blog/web-performance-monitoring-hero-times/\">Blogpost - Hero Element Timing - SpeedCurve</a></li>","updatedAt":"2020-06-23T00:06:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Interactivity metrics</h2><h3>Max Potential First Input Delay</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://web.dev/lighthouse-max-potential-fid/\">Docs - Max Potential FID - web.dev</a></li>","updatedAt":"2020-06-23T00:06:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Concepts</h2><h3>Field Data (Real User Monitoring - RUM)</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://zizzamia.github.io/perfume/\">Perfume.js</a> - Open Source Library to collect Field Data.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-06-22T15:31:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Concepts</h2><h3>Field Data (Real User Monitoring - RUM)</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/GoogleChrome/web-vitals\">Web Vitals</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/GoogleChrome/web-vitals\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">3.2k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":3246,\"repo\":\"GoogleChrome/web-vitals\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Open Source Library to collect Field Data.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-06-22T15:31:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Concepts</h2><h3>Lab Data (Synthetic Measurements)</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.sitespeed.io/\">Sitespeed.io</a> - A set of open source performance monitoring tools.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-26T07:26:44.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Concepts</h2><h3>Lab Data (Synthetic Measurements)</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://calibreapp.com\">Calibre</a> - Web performance monitoring SaaS.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-26T07:26:44.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Concepts</h2><h3>Lab Data (Synthetic Measurements)</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://treo.sh/\">treo.sh</a> - Web performance monitoring SaaS.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-26T07:26:44.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Concepts</h2><h3>Lab Data (Synthetic Measurements)</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://speedcurve.com/\">SpeedCurve</a> - Web performance monitoring SaaS.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-26T07:26:44.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Concepts</h2><h3>Field Data (Real User Monitoring - RUM)</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://speedcurve.com/features/lux/\">SpeedCurve LUX</a> - Real User Monitoring SaaS.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-26T07:26:44.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Concepts</h2><h3>Field Data (Real User Monitoring - RUM)</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.akamai.com/uk/en/products/performance/mpulse-real-user-monitoring.jsp\">Akamai mPulse</a> - Real User Monitoring SaaS.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-26T07:26:44.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Concepts</h2><h3>Field Data (Real User Monitoring - RUM)</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://sematext.com/experience/\">Sematext Experience</a> - Real User Monitoring SaaS.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-26T07:26:44.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Interactivity metrics</h2><h3>Time to Interactive (TTI)</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Field: Not recommended as users interacting with your page can skew field measurements of TTI</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T23:40:23.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Network metrics</h2><h3>TCP and SSL/TLS latency</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Lab: See <a href=\"https://www.ssllabs.com/ssltest/index.html\">Qualys SSL Labs</a> for an audit</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T23:20:25.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Network metrics</h2><h3>DNS latency</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Lab: DNS performance testing tools</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T23:19:26.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Network metrics</h2><h3>DNS latency</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Field: IE9+, Safari 9+</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T23:19:26.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Network metrics</h2><h3>TCP and SSL/TLS latency</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Field: IE9+, Safari 9+</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T23:19:26.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Network metrics</h2><h3>Time to First Byte (TTFB)</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Lab: most server load testing tools report this</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T23:19:26.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Network metrics</h2><h3>Time to First Byte (TTFB)</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Field: IE9+, Safari 9+</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T23:19:26.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Rendering metrics</h2><h3>Visually Complete</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Lab: WPT</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T23:09:27.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Rendering metrics</h2><h3>Visually Complete</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Field: N/A</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T23:09:27.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Rendering metrics</h2><h3>Visually Complete</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://sites.google.com/a/webpagetest.org/docs/using-webpagetest/metrics/speed-index\">Docs - Visually Complete - WPT</a></li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T23:09:27.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Interactivity metrics</h2><h3>Max Potential First Input Delay</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Lab: Lighthouse</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T23:09:27.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Interactivity metrics</h2><h3>Max Potential First Input Delay</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Field: N/A</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T23:09:27.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Network metrics</h2><h3>Transferred bytes</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Lab: Lighthouse (budgets), Sitespeed.io, custom tools</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T23:09:27.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Network metrics</h2><h3>Transferred bytes</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Field: N/A - but numbers usually the same as in Lab</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T23:09:27.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Network metrics</h2><h3>Transferred bytes</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.sitespeed.io/documentation/pagexray/\">Sitespeed.io PageXray</a></li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T23:09:27.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Network metrics</h2><h3>Transferred bytes</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://developers.google.com/web/tools/lighthouse/audits/budgets\">Lighthouse Performance Budgets</a></li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T23:09:27.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Network metrics</h2><h3>Transferred bytes</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://infrequently.org/2017/10/can-you-afford-it-real-world-web-performance-budgets/\">Can You Afford It?: Real-world Web Performance Budgets</a></li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T23:09:27.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Network metrics</h2><h3>Transferred bytes</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/patrickhulce/third-party-web\">Which third party scripts are most excessive</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/patrickhulce/third-party-web\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">920</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":920,\"repo\":\"patrickhulce/third-party-web\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--></li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T23:09:27.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Other metrics</h2><h3>Google PageSpeed Insights score</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://developers.google.com/speed/docs/insights/v5/about\">About PageSpeed Insights</a></li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T23:09:27.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Other metrics</h2><h3>Google PageSpeed Insights score</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://medium.com/expedia-group-tech/whats-in-the-google-pagespeed-score-a5fc93f91e91\">What's in the Google PageSpeed score</a></li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T23:09:27.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Other metrics</h2><h3>Google PageSpeed Insights score</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://calibreapp.com/blog/how-pagespeed-works/\">How Google Pagespeed works</a></li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T23:09:27.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Other metrics</h2><h3>Server Timing</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Server-Timing\">Docs - Server Timing</a></li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T23:09:27.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Other metrics</h2><h3>DOMContentLoaded</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/Events/DOMContentLoaded\">Docs - <code>DOMContentLoaded</code></a></li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T23:09:27.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Other metrics</h2><h3>window.load</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/Events/load\">Docs - <code>window.load</code></a></li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T23:09:27.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Concepts</h2><h3>User-centric metrics</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Is it happening? - Did the navigation start successfully? Has the server responded? (e.g <a href=\"https://github.com/csabapalfi/awesome-web-performance-metrics/#first-contentful-paint-fcp\">FCP</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/csabapalfi/awesome-web-performance-metrics/#first-contentful-paint-fcp\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">591</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":591,\"repo\":\"csabapalfi/awesome-web-performance-metrics\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END-->)</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T20:47:55.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Concepts</h2><h3>Critical rendering path</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://developers.google.com/web/fundamentals/performance/critical-rendering-path/\">Critical rendering path</a></li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T20:43:16.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Concepts</h2><h3>Long tasks</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/longtasks/\">Spec - Long Tasks</a></li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T20:43:16.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Concepts</h2><h3>Long tasks</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://calendar.perfplanet.com/2017/tracking-cpu-with-long-tasks-api/\">Blogpost - Tracking CPU with Long Tasks API</a></li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T20:43:16.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Concepts</h2><h3>User-centric metrics</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Is it delightful/smooth? - Are the interactions smooth and natural, free of lag and jank?</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-06T20:43:16.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Concepts</h2><h3>Lab Data (Synthetic Measurements)</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://developers.google.com/web/tools/lighthouse/\">Lighthouse</a> - A tool built on Google Chrome to audit web pages. You can run it from Chrome DevTools, a Chrome Extension or from the command line (even with headless Chrome).</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-02T10:59:14.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Concepts</h2><h3>Lab Data (Synthetic Measurements)</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://developers.google.com/speed/pagespeed/insights/\">Google PageSpeed Insights</a> - Free and hosted Lighthouse reporting (and more) by Google.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-02T10:59:14.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Concepts</h2><h3>Lab Data (Synthetic Measurements)</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.webpagetest.org/\">WebpageTest</a> - Free and hosted web performance testing (also an open source project).</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-02T10:59:14.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Concepts</h2><h3>Field Data (Real User Monitoring - RUM)</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://philipwalton.com/articles/the-google-analytics-setup-i-use-on-every-site-i-build/#performance-tracking\">Performance tracking with Google Analytics (GA)</a></li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-02T10:59:14.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Concepts</h2><h3>Field Data (Real User Monitoring - RUM)</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://developers.google.com/web/tools/chrome-user-experience-report/\">Chrome User Experience Report (CrUX)</a></li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-02T10:59:14.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Concepts</h2><h3>Field Data (Real User Monitoring - RUM)</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://developers.google.com/web/updates/2017/06/user-centric-performance-metrics#load_abandonment\">Load abandonment</a> - Track  <code>visibilitychange</code> to account for survivorship bias.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-02T10:59:14.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Interactivity metrics</h2><h3>Time to Interactive (TTI)</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1GGiI9-7KeY3TPqS3YT271upUVimo-XiL5mwWorDUD4c/edit\">Spec - TTI - Lighthouse</a></li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-02T10:59:14.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Other metrics</h2><h3>User Timing</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Lab: Lighthouse, WPT</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-02T10:59:14.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Rendering metrics</h2><h3>First Contentful Paint (FCP)</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Lab: Lighthouse</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-01T19:14:21.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Interactivity metrics</h2><h3>Time to Interactive (TTI)</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://blog.dareboost.com/en/2019/05/measuring-interactivity-time-to-interactive/\">Blogpost - TTI</a></li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-01T19:14:21.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Interactivity metrics</h2><h3>First Input Delay (FID)</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Lab: N/A (as it requires the user to interact with the page)</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-01T19:14:21.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Interactivity metrics</h2><h3>First Input Delay (FID)</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Field: IE9+ (and Safari, Chrome, Firefox) (with polyfill - 0.4KB)</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-01T19:14:21.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Interactivity metrics</h2><h3>First Input Delay (FID)</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/GoogleChromeLabs/first-input-delay\">Polyfill - FID</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/GoogleChromeLabs/first-input-delay\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">340</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":340,\"repo\":\"GoogleChromeLabs/first-input-delay\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--></li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-01T19:14:21.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Network metrics</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://developers.google.com/web/fundamentals/performance/navigation-and-resource-timing/\">Blogpost - Navigation and Resource Timing</a></li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-01T19:14:21.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Network metrics</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/navigation-timing-2/\">Spec - Navigation Timing</a></li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-01T19:14:21.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Network metrics</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/resource-timing-2/\">Spec - Resource Timing</a></li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-01T19:14:21.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Other metrics</h2><h3>User Timing</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Field: IE 10+, Safari 11+ (and Chrome, Firefox of course)</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-01T19:14:21.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Other metrics</h2><h3>User Timing</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/user-timing/\">Spec - User Timing</a></li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-01T19:14:21.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Other metrics</h2><h3>Frame rate</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Lab: Chrome and FF Devtools</li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-01T19:14:21.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Other metrics</h2><h3>Frame rate</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Field: No browser implements the Frame Timing API yet but you can roll your own fps meter using <code>requestAnimationFrame</code></li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-01T19:14:21.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Other metrics</h2><h3>Frame rate</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Frame_Timing_API\">Docs - Frame Timing API</a></li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-01T19:14:21.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Other metrics</h2><h3>Frame rate</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://developers.google.com/web/tools/chrome-devtools/evaluate-performance/#analyze_frames_per_second\">Docs - Chrome Devtools - FPS</a></li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-01T19:14:21.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Other metrics</h2><h3>Frame rate</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Tools/Performance/Frame_rate\">Docs - Firefox Developer Tools - Frame rate</a></li>","updatedAt":"2019-09-01T19:14:21.000Z"}]},"previous":{"id":"awesomes/github.com/AdrienTorris/awesome-blazor","repo":"AdrienTorris/awesome-blazor"},"next":{"id":"awesomes/github.com/aniftyco/awesome-tailwindcss","repo":"aniftyco/awesome-tailwindcss"}},"pageContext":{"repo":"csabapalfi/awesome-pagespeed-metrics","id":"awesomes/github.com/csabapalfi/awesome-pagespeed-metrics","previousId":"awesomes/github.com/AdrienTorris/awesome-blazor","nextId":"